lia (2011 film)|Melancholia]]'' || [[Lars von Trier]] || {{flag|Denmark}}\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"| ''[[Tyrannosaur (film)|Tyrannosaur]]'' || [[Paddy Considine]] || {{flag|UK}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[28th Independent Spirit Awards|2012]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''''[[Amour (2012 film)|Amour]]'''''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''[[Michael Haneke]]''' ||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | {{flag|Austria}}/{{flag|France}}/{{flag|Germany}}\n|-\n|''[[Once Upon a Time in Anatolia]]'' || ''Bir zamanlar Anadolu'da''|| [[Nuri Bilge Ceylan]] || {{flag|Turkey}}/{{flag|Bosnia and Herzegovina}}\n|-\n|''[[Rust and Bone]]'' || ''De rouille et d'os''|| [[Jacques Audiard]] || {{flag|France}}/{{flag|Belgium}}\n|-\n|''[[Sister (2012 film)|Sister]]'' || ''L'enfant d'en haut''|| [[Ursula Meier]] || {{flag|France}}/{{flag|Switzerland}}\n|-\n|''[[War Witch]]'' || ''Rebelle''|| [[Kim Nguyen]] || {{flag|Canada}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[29th Independent Spirit Awards|2013]]||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''''[[Blue Is the Warmest Colour]]'''''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''''La vie d'Ad\u00e8le'''''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''[[Abdellatif Kechiche]]''' ||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |{{flag|France}}\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"| ''[[Gloria (2013 film)|Gloria]]'' || [[Sebastian Lelio]] || {{flag|Chile}}\n|-\n|''[[The Great Beauty]]'' || ''La grande bellezza''|| [[Paolo Sorrentino]] || {{flag|Italy}}\n|-\n|''[[The Hunt (2012 film)|The Hunt]]'' || ''Jagten''|| [[Thomas Vinterberg]] || {{flag|Denmark}}\n|-\n|''[[A Touch of Sin]]'' || ''\u5929\u6ce8\u5b9a / Ti\u0101n Zh\u00f9d\u00ecng''|| [[Jia Zhangke]] || {{flag|China}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[30th Independent Spirit Awards|2014]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''''[[Ida (film)|Ida]]'''''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''[[Pawe\u0142 Pawlikowski]]''' ||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |{{flag|Poland}}\n|-\n|''[[Force Majeure