ustralia}}\n|-\n|''[[Black Rain (Japanese film)|Black Rain]]'' || ''\u9ed2\u3044\u96e8 /  Kuroi ame''|| [[Shohei Imamura]] ||  {{flag|Japan}}\n|-\n|''[[A City of Sadness]]'' || ''\u60b2\u60c5\u57ce\u5e02 / B\u0113iq\u00edng ch\u00e9ngsh\u00ec''|| [[Hou Hsiao-hsien]] || {{flag|Taiwan}}\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"| ''[[The Cook, the Thief, His Wife & Her Lover]]'' || [[Peter Greenaway]] || {{flag|France}}/{{flag|UK}}\n|-\n|''[[Freeze Die Come to Life]]'' || ''\u0417\u0430\u043c\u0440\u0438, \u0443\u043c\u0440\u0438, \u0432\u043e\u0441\u043a\u0440\u0435\u0441\u043d\u0438 / Zamri, umri, voskresni!''|| [[Vitali Kanevsky]] || {{flag|Soviet Union}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[7th Independent Spirit Awards|1991]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''''[[An Angel at My Table]]'''''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | '''[[Jane Campion]]''' ||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | {{fb|New Zealand}}/{{flag|UK}}/{{flag|Australia}}\n|-\n|''[[The Double Life of V\u00e9ronique]]'' || ''La double vie de V\u00e9ronique''|| [[Krzysztof Kie\u015blowski]] || {{flag|France}}/{{flag|Poland}}\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"| ''[[Life Is Sweet (film)|Life is Sweet]]'' || [[Mike Leigh]] || {{flag|UK}}\n|-\n|''[[Requiem for Dominic]]'' || ''Requiem f\u00fcr Dominik'' || [[Robert Dornhelm]] || {{flag|Austria}}/{{flag|France}}/{{flag|Romania}}\n|-\n|''[[Taxi Blues]]'' || ''\u0422\u0430\u043a\u0441\u0438-\u0431\u043b\u044e\u0437 / Taksi-Blyuz''|| [[Pavel Lungin]] || {{flag|Soviet Union}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[8th Independent Spirit Awards|1992]]||colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''''[[The Crying Game]]'''''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''[[Neil Jordan]]''' ||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |{{flag|UK}}\n|-\n|''[[Close to Eden]]'' || ''\u0423\u0440\u0433\u0430 / Urga''|| [[Nikita Mikhalkov]] || {{flag|Soviet Union}}\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"| ''[[Maria Novaro#Filmography|Danzon]]'' || [[Maria Novaro]] || {{flag|Mexico}}/{{flag|Spain}}\n|-\n|colspan=\"2