 Dark]]'''''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''''Danser i m\u00f8rket'''''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''[[Lars von Trier]]''' ||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | {{flag|Denmark}}\n|-\n|''[[In the Mood for Love]]'' || ''Fa yeung nin wa''|| [[Wong Kar-wai]] ||  {{flag|France}}/{{flag|Hong Kong}}\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"| ''[[Malli (film)|Malli]]'' || [[Santosh Sivan]] || {{flag|India}}\n|-\n|''[[A Time for Drunken Horses]]'' || ''Zamani baray\u00e9 masti asbha''|| [[Bahman Ghobadi]] || {{flag|Iran}}\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"| ''[[The War Zone]]'' || [[Tim Roth]] || {{flag|UK}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[17th Independent Spirit Awards|2001]]||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"|'''''[[Am\u00e9lie]]'''''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''''Le fabuleux destin d'Am\u00e9lie Poulain'''''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''[[Jean-Pierre Jeunet]]''' ||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | {{flag|France}}\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"| ''[[Amores perros]]'' || [[Alejandro Gonz\u00e1lez I\u00f1\u00e1rritu]] ||  {{flag|Mexico}}\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"| ''[[Lumumba (film)|Lumumba]]'' || [[Raoul Peck]] || {{flag|Belgium}}/{{flag|France}}/{{flag|Germany}}/{{flag|Haiti}}\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"| ''[[Sexy Beast]]'' || [[Jonathan Glazer]] || {{flag|UK}}/{{flag|Spain}}\n|-\n|''[[Together (2000 film)|Together]]'' || ''Tillsammans''|| [[Lukas Moodysson]] || {{flag|Sweden}}/{{flag|Denmark}}/{{flag|Italy}}\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|[[18th Independent Spirit Awards|2002]] ||colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"|'''''[[Y Tu Mam\u00e1 Tambi\u00e9n]]'''''||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |'''[[Alfonso Cuar\u00f3n]]''' ||style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | {{flag|Mexico}}\n|-\n|''[[Atanarjuat: The Fast Runner]]'' || ''Atanarjuat''|| [[Zacharias Kunuk]] ||  {{flag|Canada}}\n|-\n|''[[Time Out (2001 film)|Time Out]]'' || ''L'emploi du temps''|| [[Laurent Cantet]] || {{flag|France}}\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\"| ''[[Bloody Sunday (TV film)|Bloody Sunday]]'' || [[Paul Greengrass]] || {{flag|Irel